=head1 DESCRIPTION

Container for the values required to configure logging for the
pipeline. If you don't specify these values, OpenSearch Ingestion will
not publish logs from your application to CloudWatch Logs.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 CloudWatchLogDestination => L<Paws::OSIS::CloudWatchLogDestination>

The destination for OpenSearch Ingestion logs sent to Amazon CloudWatch
Logs. This parameter is required if C<IsLoggingEnabled> is set to
C<true>.


=head2 IsLoggingEnabled => Bool

Whether logs should be published.



